text: Jam Kandorna is a village located in the Jamkandorna tehsil of the Rajkot district in Gujarat, India.Jam Kandorna (two words) refers to the village, Jamkandorna (one word) to the town and tehsil. Jam Kandorna is 73.6 km from the sub-district headquarters in Jamkandorna.VillageInfo.in Jam Kandorna ==Demographics== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Total Population !! Male Population !!
